<item>
            <title>[FELIX-263] Main build fails with Maven 2.0.5 and clean local repository</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-263</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Using Maven 2.0.5 and an empty local repository I get an error building the 0.9.0-incubator-SNAPSHOT tree. I don&apos;t see this error when I use Maven 2.0.4&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Mac OS X, Java 5</environment>
        <key id="12365961">FELIX-263</key>
            <summary>Main build fails with Maven 2.0.5 and clean local repository</summary>
